LEADING celebrity stylist, Toyin Lawani says she will re-marry if her third husband, Segun Adebayo messes up. “If my husband messes up, I would still find another person and marry,” she said. Lawani made this known in the first episode of the reality TV show, The Real Housewives of Lagos.   Oga Bello praises Sanwo-Olu as 37 filmmakers get N200m…     Man of God: Bolanle Austen-Peters’ new film makes Netflix…     BBMG promises music acts greater future   The Tiannah styling boss noted that she’s unbothered about the talks about her having three children for three different men. “If my husband messes up, I would still find another person and marry if I find love and my story will be that I have four different kids for four different dads,” she said. “And if that one fucks up too, if I find love again, I will still marry again and it will be five children for five different dads.” Lawani has three children, two daughters, and a son, from three different relationships with three different men.